sequenceDiagram
  participant U as user
  participant R as Agent Runtime
  participant M as Model
  participant T as Tool Runtime
  participant S as State

  U->>R: Fix test failure
  R->>S: Read current status
  R->>M: Build context + tool protocol
  M-->>R: Present tool intent
  R->>T: Verify, authorize and execute tools
  T-->>R: Return observation
  R->>S: Append event
  R->>M: Enter the next round with new status
  M-->>R: Final answer or move on
